00:19:37,244 --> 00:19:38,445
DO YOU REALLY THINK
YOU CAN BE ANYTHING?

474
00:19:38,478 --> 00:19:39,279
I WISH
I COULD BE A SCIENTIST!

475
00:19:39,312 --> 00:19:42,315
MAYBE I GOT MY CUTIE MARK
TOO SOON.

476
00:19:42,349 --> 00:19:44,417
HEY,
WHAT'S EVERYPONY DOING?

477
00:19:44,451 --> 00:19:45,552
THIS IS MY PARTY.

478
00:19:45,585 --> 00:19:48,821
EVERYPONY IS SUPPOSED TO BE
PAYING ATTENTION TO ME!

479
00:19:48,855 --> 00:19:49,956
WHATEVER.

480
00:19:49,989 --> 00:19:53,426
WE STILL THINK YOU'RE LOSERS,
RIGHT, DIAMOND TIARA?

481
00:19:53,460 --> 00:19:55,395
BUMP, BUMP,
SUGAR...RUMP?

482
00:19:55,428 --> 00:19:56,696
NOT NOW, SILVER SPOON.

483
00:20:00,667 --> 00:20:01,968
NAME'S SCOOTALOO.

484
00:20:02,001 --> 00:20:03,603
AND I'M SWEETIE BELLE.

485
00:20:03,636 --> 00:20:06,273
APPLE BLOOM.

486
00:20:06,306 --> 00:20:07,674
[ UP-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS ]

487
00:20:07,707 --> 00:20:10,710
THIS SONG IS SO SUPER!

488
00:20:10,743 --> 00:20:12,779
[ GLASSES CLINK ]

489
00:20:12,812 --> 00:20:15,648
[ SLURPING ]

490
00:20:15,682 --> 00:20:17,984
SO, I WAS THINKING,
NOW THAT WE'RE FRIENDS --

491
00:20:18,017 --> 00:20:20,687
I MEAN,
WE ARE FRIENDS, RIGHT?

492
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:23,456
HOW COULD WE NOT BE?
WE'RE TOTALLY ALIKE.

493
00:20:23,490 --> 00:20:24,791
WE DON'T HAVE
CUTIE MARKS,

494
00:20:24,824 --> 00:20:27,794
DIAMOND TIARA AND SILVER SPOON
DRIVE US CRAZY.

495
00:20:27,827 --> 00:20:29,296
TOTALLY CRAZY!

496
00:20:29,329 --> 00:20:31,364
[ LAUGHTER ]

497
00:20:31,398 --> 00:20:32,932
WELL,
NOW THAT WE'RE FRIENDS,

498
00:20:32,965 --> 00:20:35,268
WHAT IF THE THREE OF US
WORK TOGETHER

499
00:20:35,302 --> 00:20:37,537
TO FIND OUT WHO WE ARE
AND WHAT WE'RE SUPPOSED TO BE?

500
00:20:37,570 --> 00:20:38,805
OOH! OOH!

501
00:20:38,838 --> 00:20:41,408
WE COULD FORM
OUR OWN SECRET SOCIETY.

502
00:20:41,441 --> 00:20:43,776
I'M LIKING THIS IDEA.

503
00:20:43,810 --> 00:20:46,379
A SECRET SOCIETY.
YEAH.

504
00:20:46,413 --> 00:20:47,880
WE'LL NEED A NAME FOR IT,
THOUGH.

505
00:20:49,516 --> 00:20:51,851
THE CUTIE-MARK THREE?

506
00:20:51,884 --> 00:20:54,587
THE CUTE-TASTICALLY
FANTASTICS?

507
00:20:54,621 --> 00:20:57,524
HOW ABOUT...
THE CUTIE-MARK CRUSADERS?

508
00:20:57,557 --> 00:20:58,558
IT'S PERFECT!

509
00:20:58,591 --> 00:21:00,660
THIS IS GONNA BE
SO GREAT!

510
00:21:00,693 --> 00:21:02,395
WE'RE GONNA BE
UNSTOPPABLE!

511
00:21:02,429 --> 00:21:03,663
WHAT DO YOU SAY
WE CELEBRATE

512
00:21:03,696 --> 00:21:05,398
WITH SOME OF THESE
DELICIOUS CUPCAKES?

513
00:21:05,432 --> 00:21:07,467
NOT THE CUPCAKES!

514
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:08,735
TRUST ME.

515
00:21:08,768 --> 00:21:10,937
LET'S SEE IF THERE ARE
ANY COOKIES.

516
00:21:10,970 --> 00:21:12,472
YEAH!
COME ON.

517
00:21:12,505 --> 00:21:14,641
Twilight Sparkle:
"DEAREST PRINCESS CELESTIA,

518
00:21:14,674 --> 00:21:17,610
"I AM HAPPY TO REPORT THAT ONE
OF YOUR YOUNGEST SUBJECTS

519
00:21:17,644 --> 00:21:21,013
"HAS LEARNED A VALUABLE LESSON
ABOUT FRIENDSHIP.

520
00:21:21,047 --> 00:21:22,682
"SOMETIMES THE THING YOU THINK

521
00:21:22,715 --> 00:21:25,452
WILL CAUSE YOU TO LOSE FRIENDS
AND FEEL LEFT OUT..."

522
00:21:25,485 --> 00:21:26,786
"...CAN ACTUALLY BE THE THING

523
00:21:26,819 --> 00:21:28,821
"THAT HELPS YOU MAKE
YOUR CLOSEST FRIENDS

524
00:21:28,855 --> 00:21:31,424
AND REALIZE HOW SPECIAL
YOU ARE."

525
00:21:31,458 --> 00:21:33,460
HMM.

